data.description: Welcome to 6107 Foster Brook Dr., where the home of your dreams awaits. This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence is more than just a house; it's a place where lasting memories are made. Upgraded with a newer roof and windows, this home effortlessly combines comfort and style, ensuring you'll feel right at home from the moment you step inside. The backyard is a haven for your imagination. With ample space for gardening and outdoor gatherings, it's the perfect backdrop for making cherished memories with friends and family. Beyond the comforts of your new abode, you'll find yourself conveniently situated close to Uptown Charlotte's vibrant energy and cultural attractions. For all your shopping and dining desires, Riverbend Shopping Center is just around the corner. Don't miss out on this opportunity to experience the comfort, style, and convenience this property offers. Your new beginning starts here!
